    ingredients: ["1 Avocado", "1 teaspoon avocado oil", "2 slices of halloumi or low-carb keto bread", "1/2 teaspoon everything bagel seasoning", "1 tablespoon lime juice", "1/2 cup fresh sprouts or pea shoots", "2-3 slices fresh tomato", "2 hard-boiled eggs (optional)"],
    instructions: ["Gather all of your ingredients together, if you've chosen to prepare a keto cloud bread as the base, feel free to make that first then jump to step three. Cut your halloumi cheese into 1/4-inch slices if it did not come pre-cut, and pre-heat a non-stick pan over medium heat. In a small bowl, mash avocado with lime juice and a pinch of sea salt. You can choose to add some fresh herbs or dried spices such as red pepper flakes and garlic powder if you’d like! ", "Heat a non-stick pan over medium heat and add 1 teaspoon of avocado oil, toast the keto cheese bread 1-2 minutes per side until lightly brown on both sides. Remove your cheesy bread from the heat and set it aside on a cutting board or plate to build your avocado toast. ", "To plate your fancy keto avocado toast, top the toasted halloumi cheese with 1-2 tablespoons of mashed avocado, a few slices of tomato, sports, and a sprinkle of everything seasoning! Then dig in! "],
