    id: "paleo-shakshuka-breakfast-recipe",
    title: "Paleo Shakshuka Breakfast Recipe",
    description: "One of my favorite recent recipe developments, this highly delicious casserole is a perfect easy meal prep or family-style cooking dish that can feed many hungry mouths or create several different mea",
