    ingredients: ["160g or 3 egg, whites, and yolks separated", "2.4g or ½ teaspoon baking powder", "4g or ½ tablespoon psyllium husk fiber or flaxseed, ground", "120g or 5 oz cream cheese, room temp.", "1 pinch sea salt or table salt", "Optional: sliced chives and ½ teaspoon minced garlic"],
