    ingredients: ["2 cups carrots, rough chopped", "1 cup onions, rough chopped", "1 cup celery, washed, leaves removed", "2 teaspoons grapeseed oil", "16 oz Trifecta chicken", "1 tablespoon tomato paste", "1 ⅓ cup Trifecta brown rice", "8 cups water or stock, chicken and vegetable/mushroom base, split", "1 cup Trifecta broccoli", "To taste, Salt and Black Pepper"],
